title: Views on News With Mirza Nadeem Baig.Catalan Independence Trial day 3.Pakish Tv Barcelona.
description:
The Catalan former vice president Oriol Junqueras kicked off the defendants' examinations 14 February 2019 . In day 3 of the independence trial here, in Spain's Supreme Court in Madrid, we saw him, and former minister Joaquim Forn, speaking for the first time since November 2017.The former Catalan home affairs minister Joaquim Forn testified in Spain's Supreme Court on Thursday 14 February 2019 and said that he "defended the [independence] referendum as a politician, but told Catalan police to follow court orders."
